   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <p class="- topic/p ">The purpose of the Space Hearing Conservation Program is to minimize occupational hearing loss by providing hearing protection, training, and annual hearing tests to all persons working in areas or with equipment that have noise levels equal to or exceeding an action level of 85 decibels (dB) as an 8-hour time-weighted average (TWA), or local legislative action level, whichever is more stringent.</p>
